<section class="htp--root">
  <div class="htp--header">
    <p class="htp--label">HOW TO POP IT</p>
    <h2 class="htp--title">Three minutes. One pot. One ingredient.</h2>
    <p class="htp--subtitle">However you like to pop it, the process is the same — oil, kernels, heat, lid.<br>The way popcorn was made for a hundred years before the microwave bag showed up.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="htp--content">
    <div class="htp--methods">
      <!-- METHOD 1: Stovetop -->
      <div class="htp--card">
        <div class="htp--card-top">
          <div class="htp--card-image">
            <img src="{{ 'how-to-pop-stovetop.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Stovetop pot with popcorn" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="htp--card-meta">
            <span class="htp--method-label">METHOD 1</span>
            <h3 class="htp--method-title">Stovetop</h3>
            <div class="htp--timer">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.25 3.4375H18.75M15 11.875V16.875" stroke="#00B159" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M15 26.5625C20.3503 26.5625 24.6875 22.2253 24.6875 16.875C24.6875 11.5247 20.3503 7.1875 15 7.1875C9.64974 7.1875 5.3125 11.5247 5.3125 16.875C5.3125 22.2253 9.64974 26.5625 15 26.5625Z" stroke="#00B159" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M24.6875 7.27249L21.8925 10.0675" stroke="#00B159" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <span>~ 3 minutes</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="htp--divider"></div>
        <ol class="htp--steps">
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">1</span>
            <p>Pour about <strong>4 tbsp of oil</strong> into a heavy-bottom pot (6-quart or larger).</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">2</span>
            <p>Drop in <strong>3 kernels</strong> and cover. When they pop, your oil's ready.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">3</span>
            <p>Add <strong>1/2 cup of kernels.</strong> Lower the heat slightly. Cover.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">4</span>
            <p>Shake the pot gently until the popping slows to <strong>one pop every few seconds.</strong></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">5</span>
            <p>Pour into a bowl. Salt, butter, season however you like.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <!-- METHOD 2: Whirley Pop -->
      <div class="htp--card">
        <div class="htp--card-top">
          <div class="htp--card-image">
            <img src="{{ 'how-to-pop-whirleypop.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Whirley Pop popcorn popper" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="htp--card-meta">
            <span class="htp--method-label">METHOD 2</span>
            <h3 class="htp--method-title">Whirley Pop</h3>
            <div class="htp--timer">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.25 3.4375H18.75M15 11.875V16.875" stroke="#00B159" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M15 26.5625C20.3503 26.5625 24.6875 22.2253 24.6875 16.875C24.6875 11.5247 20.3503 7.1875 15 7.1875C9.64974 7.1875 5.3125 11.5247 5.3125 16.875C5.3125 22.2253 9.64974 26.5625 15 26.5625Z" stroke="#00B159" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M24.6875 7.27249L21.8925 10.0675" stroke="#00B159" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <span>~ 3 minutes</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="htp--divider"></div>
        <ol class="htp--steps">
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">1</span>
            <p>Add <strong>1-3 tbsp of oil</strong> and <strong>1/2 cup of kernels</strong> to the popper.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">2</span>
            <p>Place over <strong>medium heat.</strong></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">3</span>
            <p>Turn the handle <strong>slowly and steadily.</strong></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">4</span>
            <p>When popping slows — or the <strong>handle gets hard to turn</strong> — you're done.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="htp--step-num">5</span>
            <p>Pour out, season, eat.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Good to Know -->
    <div class="htp--callout">
      <h3 class="htp--callout-title">Good to Know</h3>
